<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">We are excited to announce that Academic Start completion certificates are now available to all Pathway students who finished Academic Start with a passing grade (D- or above) in each course. The certificate will be mailed to students who meet the requirements </span><strong style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;"><em>and</em></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;"> apply to receive it. &nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">To obtain the certificate, you must submit the "Application of Pathway Completion" form found at </span><a href="http://www.byui.edu/student-records/pathway-application" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">http://www.byui.edu/student-records/pathway-application</a><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">. This is a short application and can be completed and submitted entirely online. You will be asked to enter your name as it should appear on the certificate and provide a mailing address to which it will be sent. &nbsp; </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">If there are concerns about the postal system in your area, we encourage you to visit with the Pathway missionaries. They may provide you with an alternate address (such as the stake center, institute building, or their own address) to which your certificate can be mailed. &nbsp; </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Any questions regarding the completion certificate should be directed to the Online Support Center at </span><a href="mailto:onlinelearning@byui.edu" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">onlinelearning@byui.edu</a><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;"> or 1-866-672-2984.</span></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="Component" Component="x18360" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="News" label="News" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="NewsNavigationComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_ContentSnippet" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" Component="" CompTypes="ContentSnippet"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ContentSnippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" CompTypes="ContentSnippet"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x17147" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl"/></NewsDetail>
